---
import Layout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Subscription confirmed";
---
<Layout title={title} description="Your Survive the AI subscription is active. Use the guided next-step path into the playbook, Start Here, and the reporting archive.">
  <main class="bg-white py-14 text-neutral-900 sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" data-testid="newsletter-confirmed-page">
      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Confirmed</p>
        <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold text-neutral-900 sm:text-4xl">{title}</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-neutral-700">
          You&apos;re on the list. STA will send the weekly briefing, and your welcome email points you back into the playbook path without
          hiding the reporting archive behind a gate.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Step 1</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-neutral-900">Open the playbook path</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
            Use the free starter path for work, family, and focus checklists instead of hunting through the whole archive first.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            <a class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 underline underline-offset-4" href="/playbook">Go to the playbook</a>
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Step 2</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-neutral-900">Use Start Here</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
            If you want the short version of how STA is organized, Start Here gives the guided map before you dive deeper.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            <a class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 underline underline-offset-4" href="/start-here">Open Start Here</a>
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Step 3</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-neutral-900">Browse the reporting</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
            The archive stays public. Use it when you want the full reporting trail behind the weekly briefing and the playbook guidance.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            <a class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 underline underline-offset-4" href="/posts">Browse the library</a>
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
